wekurwadziwa nehurwere

0:00:21.300,0:00:22.520
Kumbira Mwari kuti akupe nyasha.

0:00:22.520,0:00:26.640
Ndipei nyasha, Ishe, kuti ndisave chituta pamusoro pekutenda kwangu

0:00:26.640,0:00:41.760
pandinenge ndiri pakumakidzwa kana makakatanwa emiedzo ye kurwara, nhamo ne zvipingamupinyi

0:00:58.300,0:01:04.340
Chero zvauri kutarisana nekumanikidzwa nazvo pasi pemuedzo, kumbira Mwari, Ishe Jesu,

0:01:04.340,0:01:13.580
Ndipei nyasha, Ishe, kuti ndisave chituta pamusoro pe kutenda kwangu pandinenge ndiri pakumakidzwa nemiedzo yemamiriro ezvinhu.

0:01:13.580,0:01:15.940
Mamiriro ezvinhu ako arisei?

0:01:15.940,0:01:22.100
Kana mamiriro ezvinhu auya, tinoita setino kanganwa kuti tiri maKristu.

0:01:48.280,0:01:50.320
Muzita raJesu Kristu.

0:01:50.320,0:01:51.200
[Ameni]

0:01:51.200,0:02:08.820
Unoita sokuti unokanganwa, kana watarisana nedambudziko, mamiriro ezvinhu, kuti uri zvinotaurwa naMwari kuti uri;

0:02:08.820,0:02:13.040
unogona kuita zvinotaurwa naMwari kuti unogona kuzviita.

0:02:13.040,0:02:18.480
Unoita sokuti unokanganwa kuti une zvinotaurwa naMwari kuti unazvo.

0:02:18.480,0:02:23.400
Mwari kana anewe, zvose zvinobvira.

0:02:23.400,0:02:29.480
Unoita sokuti unokanganwa izvozvo apo unenge watarisana nemamiriro ezvinhu.

0:02:32.420,0:02:35.440
Iwe na Mwari pamwechete.

0:02:35.440,0:02:43.260
Unoita sokunge unokanganwa kuti iwe naMwari munogona kusimudza makomo kana watarisana nematambudziko.

0:02:43.260,0:02:45.720
Unofanira kuuya pamwechete; iwe nani?

0:02:45.720,0:02:47.360
[Mwari.]

0:02:47.360,0:02:51.660
Iwe na Mwari munofanira kuve pamwe chete, kubatana maoko pamwe chete.

0:02:51.660,0:02:57.780
Hapana kana gomo, uye hakuchazove gomo

0:02:57.780,0:03:04.900
Iwe na Mwari- asi unoita seunokanganwa izvi kana watarisana nechii?

0:03:04.900,0:03:06.680
Chinetso.

0:03:06.680,0:03:16.800
Unofanira kuyeuka zvinhu zvakaoma zvikuru nenguva yekuedzwa yawasangana nayo kare.

0:03:16.800,0:03:25.260
Kiyi yekubudirira muupenyu kana uri mwana waMwari - chero nguva pane dambudziko

0:03:25.260,0:03:33.720
kurumidza kuyeuka nguva dzakange dzakoma nemiedzo mikuru yawatarisana nayo kare

0:03:33.720,0:03:43.080
Izvi zvichakupa simba kuti utarisane nechinetso chiri pamberi pako izvozvi.

0:03:48.440,0:03:50.680
Nyatsotora nguva yako kurangarira.

0:03:50.680,0:03:54.700
Izvi ndizvo zvakaitika kuna Dhavhidhi.

0:03:54.700,0:03:59.500
Dhavhidhi akafamba zvakaisvonakisa achienda kuna mambo, akati,

0:03:59.500,0:04:06.640
'Mambo, ndiri kuenda kunotarisana naGoriyati uyo ari kunetsa hama dzangu ne nyika'.

0:04:06.640,0:04:09.440
Mambo akamutarisa: 'Ndiwe aniko?'

0:04:09.440,0:04:16.920
Akati, 'Ini ndakashandisa maoko angu ega kuuraya bere'.

0:04:16.920,0:04:30.640
Apo murume uyu akauya kuzovavhiringira nyika yavo, akakurumidza kurangarira nguva yakaona chinetso nemuedzo yaakakunda.

0:04:30.640,0:04:38.780
Paakarangarira bere, akatarira Goriyati akati, "regai ndinotarisana nemurume uyu".

0:04:38.780,0:04:45.340
Nenzira imwe cheteyo,ndiwo musimboti wekuti ukunde mamiriro ezvinhu iyezvino.

0:04:45.340,0:04:51.620
Udza waugere naye, "Uyu ndiwo musimboti wekuti ndikunde mamiriro ezvinhu aripo".

0:04:51.620,0:04:56.440
Unogona kushandisa musimboti umwechetewo kuvhura nekuzarira.

0:04:56.440,0:05:03.260
Yeuka sezvo Dhavhidhi akayeuka, nekufamba zvakaisvonakisisa kuna mambo.

0:05:03.260,0:05:07.680
Tora nguva yako.

0:05:07.680,0:05:18.460
Chero nguva yauenge watarisana nedambudziko kana mamiriro ezvinhu, yeuka zvikuru zvakaoma uye nenguva yemiedzo

0:05:18.460,0:05:24.240
yawaive nayo kare ukakunda

0:05:24.240,0:05:34.700
Izvozvo zvichakupa simba kuti utarisane nechinetso chiri pamberi pako izvozvi.

0:05:34.700,0:05:42.220
Handizivi chandingagone kutarisana nacho zvino chingave chikuru kudarika zvandakambotarisana nazvo kare.

0:05:42.220,0:05:43.080
Muri kuona?

0:05:43.080,0:05:46.400
Nenzira imwe cheteyo, handizivi kuti chii chaunga tarisana nacho ikozvino

0:05:46.400,0:05:49.900
chingave chikuru kudarika icho wakapfuura machiri kare.

0:05:49.900,0:05:57.140
Paunoyeuka izvi, zvichakupa simba rekuti utarisane nezviripo izvozvi.

0:05:57.140,0:06:05.340
Unorangarira - pakati nepakati pevaripano takabva kumamisha, kana kutoti makumi mapfumbamwe kubva muzana 90% evanhu pano.

0:06:05.340,0:06:10.840
Unofanira kurangarira mazuva iwayo pawakanga uchinwa mvura inetsvina

0:06:10.840,0:06:19.400
Asi nhasi urikunwa mvura yakachena, asi - yero fivha.

0:06:22.100,0:06:26.140
Iyezvino urikunwa mvura yakachena

0:06:26.140,0:06:30.200
Saka yero fivha irikubvepi?

0:06:30.200,0:06:33.340
Ndiudze.

0:06:33.340,0:06:36.920
Iwe, iwe wakabva kumamisha.

0:06:36.920,0:06:46.060
Rangarira - pamazuva iwayo, pawaibika muriwo, uchiramba uchiudziyisa kwemazuva gumi.

0:06:46.060,0:06:50.720
Paiwanyanya kuudziyisa ndipo pawaibva wanyanya kunaka.

0:06:57.280,0:07:00.140
Ungadziyisa muriwo here nhasi?

0:07:00.140,0:07:03.660
Kana ukabika muriwo nhasi, ungaudziyisa here mangwana kuti udye zvakare?

0:07:03.660,0:07:04.920
[Kwete]

0:07:04.920,0:07:07.380
Asi kumamisha....

0:07:07.380,0:07:12.340
Ndizvo zvinhu zvakakukudza

0:07:12.340,0:07:15.160
Rangaririra mazvarirwo ako.

0:07:15.160,0:07:21.380
Vazhinji venyu havana kuzvarirwa kuchipatara.

0:07:21.380,0:07:27.840
Vanhu vaunodaidza kuti vavengi zvino, ndivo vaikupa chekudya pawaiva uri mwana.

0:07:27.840,0:07:36.900
Amai vako voga havaigona kukuchengeta - waizosiiwa uchifamba famba kune vakakupoteredza,

0:07:36.900,0:07:43.480
asi nhasi wave kuvaona sevanhu vanogona kukuuraya.

0:07:43.480,0:07:46.840
Ndihwo usimboti wandirikukupai nhasi.

0:07:46.840,0:07:58.640
Chero nguva yauenge watarisana nedambudziko kana mamiriro ezvinhu, yeuka zvakaoma zvikuru uye nenguva yemiedzo yawaive nayo kare.

0:07:58.640,0:08:00.860
Izvi zvichakupa chii?

0:08:00.860,0:08:02.760
[Simba]

0:08:02.760,0:08:05.120
Kuitei?

0:08:05.120,0:08:07.020
Kutarisana nei?

0:08:07.020,0:08:09.440
Kutarisana nemamiriro aripo izvozvi.

0:08:09.440,0:08:11.820
Unoda simba.

0:08:17.320,0:08:19.740
Uri kutaura nezve mushando wako?

0:08:19.740,0:08:23.680
Yeuka mhando yechikoro chawakapinda kumusha.

0:08:23.680,0:08:26.160
Chikoro chisina denga.

0:08:26.160,0:08:27.420
Chikoro chisina chii?

0:08:27.420,0:08:29.080
[Denga]

0:08:29.080,0:08:38.120
Wakadzidza ikoko pasi pemvura, pasi pezuva - asi tarira nhasi pane zvawave.

0:08:38.120,0:08:43.980
Kana usisazive mhando yechikoro chawakapinda kumusha mumazuva iwayo - dzokera kumusha

0:08:43.980,0:08:49.500
uone parikudzidzira vana ivavo ikozvino.

0:08:49.500,0:08:52.140
Izvi ndizvo zvinhu zvaunoisa pamwechete.

0:08:52.140,0:08:56.640
Paunofunga nezvose izvi, uchaziva kuti hapana chingakutadzisa.

0:08:56.640,0:09:03.240
Iti, " Ini chete ndini ndinogona kuzvimisa pachangu; hapana anogona kundimisa."

0:09:03.240,0:09:07.440
Hapana munhu angakutadzisa iwe; ndiwe wega unogona kuzvimisa pachako.

0:09:07.440,0:09:14.420
Kana pasina akakumisa ipapo, zvino, hapana angakumisa.

0:09:19.660,0:09:25.920
Unoda simba rekuti uende mberi.

0:09:25.920,0:09:30.740
Izvi ndizvo zvandinozvirera nazvo

0:09:30.740,0:09:42.100
Hazvinei chero chinouya kwandiri, Ndinogara pasi kutarira zvakamboitika kunzvimbo yandinobva,

0:09:42.100,0:09:44.340
zvandakapfuura mazviri

0:09:44.340,0:09:51.960
Chero zvinoitika zvino, ndinonyemwerera ndobva ndati, "Uri mwana".

0:09:55.520,0:09:57.600
ndinonyemwerera.

0:09:57.600,0:10:07.740
Ukangorega kuchinjanisa mufaro wako nemamiriro ezvinhu, unokunda.

0:10:07.740,0:10:14.020
Udza waugere naye, "Rega kutsinhanisa mufaro wako nemamiriro ezvinhu"

0:10:14.020,0:10:19.440
Ukangorega kuchinjanisa mufaro wako nemamiriro ezvinhu, unokunda.

0:10:19.440,0:10:24.480
nekuti unoda mufaro kuti ukurire mamiriro ezvinhu.

0:10:24.480,0:10:30.700
Hazvinei kuti mamiriro ezvinhu akakura sei, kana ukasatsinhanisa mufaro wako ne mamiriro ezvinhu, uchakunda.

0:10:30.700,0:10:34.740
Asi kana mufaro ukaenda, haugoni kukunda mamiriro ezvinhu.

0:10:34.740,0:10:37.540
Izvi ndizvo mamariro ezvinhu anoda kukukutorera.

0:10:37.540,0:10:39.940
Zvinoda kukutorera mufaro wako.

0:10:39.940,0:10:41.200
Mwari wangu.

0:10:41.200,0:10:44.100
Zvinoda kukuona wakasuwa.

0:10:44.100,0:10:45.900
Mamiriro ezvinhu anoda kukuona wakaita sei?

0:10:45.900,0:10:46.600
[Wakasuwa]

0:10:46.600,0:10:49.940
Anoda kukuona wakasuwa

0:10:49.940,0:10:53.280
Apo mamamiriro azvinhu akauya, achiona wakasuwa...

0:10:53.280,0:10:55.300
Ndichapfuura sei mune izvi?

0:10:55.300,0:10:56.760
O Mwari wangu.

0:10:56.760,0:10:59.060
Izvi zvakandinyanyira zvikuru.

0:10:59.060,0:11:02.320
Pasi pemamiriro ezvinhu akadaro, haugoni kunyengetera.

0:11:02.320,0:11:05.500
Pasi pemamiriro ezvinhu akadaro, haukwanisi kufunga nezva Mwari.

0:11:05.500,0:11:11.220
Pasi pemamiriro ezvinhu iwayo....

0:11:11.220,0:11:21.200
Pakarepo ucharasikirwa ne mafungiro chaiwo, wese akakupoteredza ndiye muvengi wako.

0:11:21.200,0:11:24.440
Hauzokwanisa kupa zvako zvese.

0:11:24.440,0:11:33.360
Ndinosimudza foni:- Haro-Imba yako irikutsva

0:11:33.360,0:11:39.440
-Urikureva imba yangu here?- Hongu. Zvakaipisisa. Vadzimuri varipo.

0:11:39.440,0:11:42.600
Kare ndange ndichinyemwerera.

0:11:49.700,0:11:53.480
Vanhu vakandipoteredza vobva vati, "Chii chaitika zvino?"

0:11:53.480,0:11:54.780
Ndiri kuuya.

0:11:54.780,0:11:58.540
Ndatsinhanisa chii?

0:11:58.540,0:11:59.940
[Mufaro]

0:11:59.940,0:12:00.660
Nechii?

0:12:00.660,0:12:02.200
[ Mamiriro ezvinhu]

0:12:06.760,0:12:09.300
Zvitarise-urikufara iko zvino.

0:12:09.300,0:12:13.320
satani anoziva zvaanogona kuita kumisa mufaro iwowo.

0:12:13.320,0:12:15.700
Anoziva

0:12:15.700,0:12:20.280
Umwe munhu anoda kukuona pauri kutamba.

0:12:20.280,0:12:22.080
Kupi?

0:12:22.080,0:12:23.400
Ndionei

0:12:25.400,0:12:26.700
Kupi?

0:12:29.620,0:12:34.040
Usazviite nyore kuna satani.

0:12:34.040,0:12:36.500
Umwe munhu arikukurwisa.

0:12:36.500,0:12:43.040
Unozorora pachinzvimbo chekurwisana nazvo - unozvichipisa

0:12:43.040,0:12:47.560
Pane umwe munhu arikuda kukuona apo uchiri kutamba.

0:12:47.580,0:12:50.700
Kupi?

0:12:50.700,0:12:53.200
Zvakanaka,ikoko . Ndiri kuuya.

0:12:53.200,0:12:56.440
Urikuda kupedzisa kutamba kwako.

0:12:56.440,0:12:58.820
Vangani venyu  vangaite izvi?

0:12:58.820,0:13:03.680
Wati wambopedza kutamba usati wapanguva kune umwe munhu aida kukuona here?

0:13:03.680,0:13:06.880
Kwete, ndinokuzivai.

0:13:06.880,0:13:14.360
Saka rega kutsinhanisa mufaro wako nemamiriro ezvinhu

0:13:14.360,0:13:24.180
Kana uine marwadzo akanyanya muruoko rwako, unogona kusarudza kusatsinhanisa marwadzo ako nemufaro wako

0:13:24.180,0:13:25.440
Wakadii?

