Apo pane marwadzo ne mufaro uripo, marwadzo haazogari.

0:13:54.620,0:14:01.760
Apo pane kusuwa ne mufaro uripo, mufaro haazogari zvachose.

0:14:01.760,0:14:04.220
Hazvionani

0:14:04.220,0:14:07.680
Sezvinoita  kitsi nagonzo.

0:14:07.680,0:14:14.700
Kana ukasarudza kuva nemufaro apo uri kutsvaga basa,uchakurumidza kuriwana.

0:14:18.100,0:14:29.980
Kana uchirwara, kana ukagona kusarudza kufara mumwoyo mako - kurwara ikoko hakuzogari nguva refu.

0:14:29.980,0:14:36.480
Kana muchato wako uri pasi pechityiso, uye mumwe munhu ari kuedza kuupidigura

0:14:36.480,0:14:40.480
sarudza kufara, uone kuti zvii zvinozoitika pamberi.

0:14:40.480,0:14:47.020
Unoziva here kuti mamiriro ezvinhu ndiwo anosangana nemufaro; hausi mufaro unosangana nemamiriro ezvinhu.

0:14:47.020,0:14:54.740
Taurira waugere naye "mamiriro ezvinhu anosangana ne mufaro; mufaro hausangane nemamiriro ezvinhu."

0:14:54.740,0:14:59.420
Kana ukadzidza hupenyu hwako, mamiriro ezvinhu ndiwo anosangana ne mufaro.

0:14:59.420,0:15:04.840
Muupenyu hwemunhu, mamiriro ezvinhu anouya ku mufaro.

0:15:04.840,0:15:10.760
Mufaro ndiwo murudzi wako; mamiriro ezvinhu haasi muridzi wako.

0:15:10.760,0:15:12.980
Mamiriro ezvinhu anosangana ne mufaro.

0:15:12.980,0:15:15.720
Kana nyoka ichiuya mumba mako unopfiga musiwo.

0:15:15.720,0:15:20.600
Haumhanye kuno zarurira nyoka mukova.

0:15:20.600,0:15:24.220
Regai kutsinhanisa mufaro wako ne chii?

0:15:24.220,0:15:25.880
[Mamiriro ezvinhu]

0:15:25.880,0:15:39.140
Kana ukaita izvi, mamiriro ezvinhu anouya asi haazogari uye uchadzidza chidzidzo chine simba chichakubatsira.

0:15:44.300,0:15:48.260
Tarisai kare kwangu kubva pakutanga.

0:15:48.260,0:15:52.340
Zita reushumiri runo haarafanira kuva "Church of all Nations".

