unogona kumira wakapfava kuti Mwari akusunungure."

0:16:58.560,0:17:08.180
Asi kana usingaziva kwauri kuenda, unozvisungura wega

0:17:11.240,0:17:13.720
Wange uchizvisunungura wega

0:17:13.720,0:17:21.240
Unozvisunungura mubhizimisi, mumuchato, muma chechi, kwese kwese urikungo......

0:17:21.240,0:17:22.700
Nyadzi idzi ...

0:17:22.700,0:17:24.440
Sei ari kunyepa pamusoro pezvangu?

0:17:24.440,0:17:25.680
Wobva wafamba uchibva ipapo

0:17:25.680,0:17:32.560
Unofamba kubva munharaunda, bhizimisi, chechi kana muchato.

0:17:32.560,0:17:34.220
Imhandoi yekutuka uku?

0:17:34.220,0:17:37.120
Izvi zvino nyadzisa, handigoni kutenda zvauri kutaura.

0:17:37.120,0:17:40.720
Sei mufundisi uyu ari kureva nhema pamusoro pangu?

0:17:40.720,0:17:44.840
Unobuda mukereke.

0:17:44.840,0:17:49.320
Mumuchato zvakare - murume wangu akanyepa pamusoro pezvangu!

0:17:49.320,0:17:51.260
Sei mukadzi wangu akaita izvi kwandiri.

0:17:51.260,0:17:54.600
Unobuda kubva mumuchato.

